    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In Christi nomine. Anno eiusdem nativitatis millesimo centesimo
                        quinquagesimo prim[o, tempore] <persName key="#Popes" ref="#people/409"
                            >Eugenii</persName> pape et <persName key="#Emperor/king"
                            ref="#people/126">Conradi</persName> [imperatoris, die ...] | mense
                        madii, indiccione quartadecima, in <placeName ref="#places/3524"
                            >Cornetho</placeName>. Omnibus manifestum est atque congrua rac[i]one
                        disp[ositum libenter] debere eorum desideriis annuere pro quibus et
                        venerabilium locis utilitatibus meliorandique causa proficiunt. E[t ideo]
                        vos quidem in Dei nomine domnus <persName key="#Abbots" ref="#people/4310"
                            >Iohannes</persName> Dei gratia <rs key="#Abbots">habbas</rs>
                        <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Houses #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Fundi #Casalia #Landed_possessions #Forests #Fisheries #Penalty #Cereals #Wine #Hay/fodder #Rent_in_money #Notary #Missus #Plebs #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Churches #Monasteries"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1460">Sancte Maria que vocatur de <placeName
                                ref="#places/4179">Ponposia</placeName></orgName> largitori, ideo
                            <rs key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis">iure enp[hiteo]ticario</rs>
                        concedisti rem iuris proprietatis monasterio vestro nobis presentibus
                                <persName><name ref="Iordanus Dalbuso">Zordano qui vocatur
                                Dalbuso</name></persName> et <persName><name ref="Marcus"
                                >Marcii</name></persName> germanis enfite[utis peti]toribus, pro nos
                        et pro <persName><name ref="Heito">Heito </name></persName> et
                                <persName><name ref="Elias">Helia</name></persName> germani nostri
                        nostrisque filiis et nepotibus tantum, qui abitare videmus in loco qui
                        dicitur Alb[…], quantascumque habemus et detinemus per anteriorem enfiteosis
                        in <rs key="#Fundi">fundo</rs> qui vocatur <geogName
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Houses #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Fundi #Casalia #Landed_possessions #Forests #Fisheries #Penalty #Cereals #Wine #Hay/fodder #Rent_in_money #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                            ref="#estates/2437">
                            <placeName
                                key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Houses #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Fundi #Casalia #Landed_possessions #Forests #Fisheries #Penalty #Cereals #Wine #Hay/fodder #Rent_in_money #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                                ref="#places/3541">Gragnano</placeName></geogName> et ubicumque
                        nobis pertinet per [singula] vel diversa loca. Que omnia cum <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">terris</rs>, <rs key="#Wine">vineis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Houses">casis</rs> et <rs key="#Casalia">casalibus</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Cereals">campis</rs>, <rs key="#Hay/fodder">pratis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Hay/fodder">passculis</rs>, <rs key="#Forests">silvis</rs>,
                            <rs>salectis</rs>, <rs key="#Marshes/lagoons/tombolos">palu[dibus</rs>,
                            <rs key="#Fisheries">pi]|scacionibus</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters">venacionibus</rs> et cum
                        omnibus ad prescriptas res pertinentibus, constituto <rs key="#Fines"
                            >territorio</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Fines" ref="#places/3522"><geogName key="#Fines"
                                ref="#estates/2420">Adriensis</geogName></placeName>, <rs
                            key="#Plebs">plebe</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Houses #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos 
                            #Fundi #Casalia #Landed_possessions #Forests #Fisheries #Penalty #Cereals #Wine #Hay/fodder #Rent_in_money 
                            #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Plebs"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1496">Sancte Andre[e qui vocatur] de
                            Archoata</orgName>. Dum nobis superius nominatis enphyteuti petitoribus
                        atque filiis et nepotibus nostris divina gratia in hac lu[ce i]usserit
                        permanere concedisti eam rem que superius legitur ad habendum, tenendum,
                        possidendum, fruendum, defensandum [et in] omnibus meliorandum. Et annualem
                        pensionem persolvendam omni mense marcio <rs key="#Rent_in_money">denarios
                            tres Veronenses</rs>. Idcirco enim dedis[ti nobis in]vestitorem
                            <persName key="#Missus"><name ref="Sichelmus">
                            Sichelmo</name></persName> vestro <rs key="#Missus">misso</rs>, qui nos
                        in prescriptas res in vestra vice corporaliter investiat. Nec licenciam
                        h[abemus] de prescriptas res in alico venerabile locum relinquere nisi ad
                        prenominato monasterio <rs key="#Churches">ecclesię</rs> Ponposiane. Que
                        omni[a si non] observare et adimplere promittimus pro nos et pro germani
                        nostri nostrisque filiis et nepotibus vos vestrisque s[uccessoribus], sub
                        pene nomine <rs key="#Penalty">unciam unius auri</rs> et post penam solutam,
                        maneat firma hec paginam enphyteosis. [Quam vero] paginam enfiteosis
                            <persName key="Notary"><name ref="Pasquale">Passcalem</name></persName>
                        in Dei nomine <rs key="#Notary">notarium</rs> Ponposianem hecclesie
                        scribendum rogavi et manu mea [firmavi], in die et indiccione prescripta. +
                        + Signa manuum prescriptorum enfiteuticarum petitorum confirmancium ad omnia
                        prescripta. Ad hec fuerunt testes presentes: Guidonis qui vocatur Linghitta,
                        Zorzo, Andrea de Sta[…], Rainerius da Rudigi, Pizolus da Gragnano, Cauchus
                        et Calianus testis rogatis ad omnia prescripta.</ab>
